	<h1 class="display-4">Amazon WorkSpaces Cost Optimisation</h1>

	<p class="lead">
		The Amazon WorkSpaces Cost Optimisation provides a detailed view of 
		Amazon WorkSpaces usage, providing customers with the insights required 
		to make decisions around cost optimisation.
	</p>

